- content_for :html_head do
- content_for :title, "Audit Prep"

h1 style="font-family: 'Canela'; font-size: 30px; font-weight: 400;"
  | Audit Prep
= link_to '#', "data-target": "#modal", "data-toggle": "modal", "data-remote": true do
  .pull-right style='padding: 16px;position: absolute;right: 0;background-color: #FFCC01;border-radius: 50% 0 0 50%; color: #000000'
    span style="border: 1px solid;border-radius: 50%;padding: 0px 10px;font-size: 19px;font-weight: 400;right: 23px;"
      | i
.row
.col-md-7.p-l-0
  .well.m-t-1 style="border: 2px solid #000; color: #00000; font-weight: 400"
    | Start your regulatory examination off on the right foot by being able to respond to their document request list in a prompt manner. Regulators  may consider slow or imprecise document production to be a red flag. So, prepare yourself for an examination by understanding what they will likely ask for and having it ready at your fingertips.

.row
.col-md-7.p-l-0
  .panel.panel-default
    .panel-heading
      .pull-left
        h3 Sample Document Request List
      .pull-right
        .btn-group
          = link_to "Save", "#", class: "btn btn-primary btn-solid p-y-0"
      .clearfix
    / hr.m-y-0
    .panel-content-wrapper style="height: 575px; padding: 11px 18px;"
      = render partial: 'sample_document'
.col-md-5.p-l-0
  .panel.panel-default
    .panel-heading
      .pull-left
        h3 Books & Records
      .pull-right
        .btn-group
          = link_to "Add", "#", class: "btn btn-primary btn-solid p-y-0"

      .clearfix
    .panel-content-wrapper style="height: 575px; padding: 11px 18px;"
      table.table.table-striped.table-blue
        thead
          tr
            th Name
            th 
            th Modified
            th 
            th 
            th 
            th 
        tbody
          - for i in 1..10 do
            tr
              td
                = link_to '#', "data-target": "#modal", "data-toggle": "modal", "data-remote": true do
                  i.fa.fa-folder style='font-size: 40px; color: dodgerblue'
              td
                | Annual Reviews
              td
                = DateTime.current.strftime '%b %-d, %Y'
              td
                = link_to '#', "data-target": "#modal", "data-toggle": "modal", "data-remote": true do
                  i.fa.fa-random
              td
                = link_to '#', "data-target": "#modal", "data-toggle": "modal", "data-remote": true do
                  i.icon-cloud-download
              td
                = link_to '#', "data-target": "#modal", "data-toggle": "modal", "data-remote": true do
                  i.icon-note
              td
                = link_to '#' do
                  i.icon-trash